Packages
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator The entry point of the data generator application; it contains the main method.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller Represents the controller of the MVC pattern; it's not allowed to get access to the data model directly, instead use this package to do so.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.algorithm Used algorithms are put in here.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.boot Links to external files are defined here; a file is said to be external, if and only if it doesn't reside in a *.jar file.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration Everything needed to generated proper data is seeded in this package.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.dependency Some attributes (facets) rely on values of other attributes; in other words, the depend on those attributes.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.distribution To make data generation flexible and not static, random data is used; This data is calculated by probability distributions.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.filltype Specifies different types to 'fill' attributes with data or values, respectively.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.datageneration.unit A unit is a standardized weight or measurement that describes the generated entity more precisly.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.io Everything that has to do with serialization or deserialization is in this package.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.log This package is responsible for handling exceptions and errors.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.controller.worker Long running background tasks for I/O, database or any other computational intensive task are separated from the EDT.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.model Represents the data model of MVC pattern; therefore, the data structures used in this application are stored here.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.model.datastructure Contains the Meta-Meta-Model artefact class describing the EMF Ecore Meta-Model.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view Represents the view of the MVC pattern and interacts with the user through a UI.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view.dialog All dialog frames are in this package.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view.graph Graphical components to visualized all sorts of things; here it visualizes probability functions.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view.message Messages caused either due to errors, information, input, query etc are created with predefined methods.
de.uni.bamberg.wiai.minf.forflow.datagenerator.view.util Utilities which are used by the view layer, but do not fit into any of the previous packages.
